name: When Theres No More Room In Hell Compilation
description:
"When There's No More Room In Hell Volume I" This two CD compilation is a cross-section of some of the sickest, ruthless, and most wicked flavor the world of underground hip hop has to offer! In total 38, yep that’s right 38 slamming tracks included on this two cd compilation! The musical styles contained here are known by many different names as people feebly attempt to categorize it but can't! This is the flavor that beneath the radar, stemming from all walks of life and appealing to many different types of people! Once purely found only in the underground, the appeal is growing everyday proving every year why it is here to stay!

All of the artists listed here have given this compilation a exclusive song for this compilation only! Its our hope that this will help spread the word of other artists to localized pockets of fans, and help make the scene stronger! Trying to turn on fans of one artist to a whole other world of artists that they didn’t even know existed! By keeping all the tracks exclusive and keeping the costs low, we hope to do our part to keep the wicked underground growing stronger every day!

If you haven't got your copy of "When There's No More Room In Hell Volume I" what are you waiting for? This two CD compilation includes all exclusive tracks from Big B, Danny Diablo Ft. La Coka Nostra, DJ Q-Ball from the BloodHound Gang, P.L.C., WOLFPAC, Q-Strange, Killa C and much much more! Two CD's with thirty eight tracks for only $10.00!
